		<td><b>Strange Mario/Duck Hunt board...</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I was applying DeOxit to more of my collection this evening and noticed a mario/duck hunt cartridge I had looked totally different from what I'm used to seeing. Usually you see a big PRG-ROM, CHR-ROM, and for mario/duck hunt a couple of extra chips.  This one had four, flattened, round, black objects very flat against the board. Is anyone familiar with this sort of board? If not perhaps I will post a photo.

		

